my daughter Ann on Christmas.

01:40:50.498 --> 01:40:53.262
You winked at her?
Do you remember?

01:40:53.334 --> 01:40:55.859
Oh, yeah.
I remember you two.

01:40:55.937 --> 01:40:58.428
I know what you told her,
and she hasn't been the same since.

01:40:58.506 --> 01:40:59.905
I'm sorry.
Can I have the driver's license?

01:40:59.974 --> 01:41:01.498
You might have been right.

01:41:01.576 --> 01:41:04.272
It hasn't been perfect, ok?

01:41:04.345 --> 01:41:05.778
Hey, nobody's perfect.

01:41:05.846 --> 01:41:07.609
Exactly. I make mistakes.
That's what I was saying.

01:41:07.682 --> 01:41:11.345
Sometimes maybe
I'm a little bit selfish.

01:41:11.419 --> 01:41:14.047
Maybe sometimes
I'm a little bit irresponsible,

01:41:14.121 --> 01:41:16.351
and the lights go out sometimes.

01:41:16.424 --> 01:41:18.756
But I'm trying.
That's the point, right?

01:41:18.826 --> 01:41:20.623
I am trying. It's not easy.

01:41:20.695 --> 01:41:22.458
I'm sure it's not easy for her, either.

01:41:22.530 --> 01:41:24.498
If I could get
the driver's license from you?

01:41:24.565 --> 01:41:26.396
I know I should have
helped her find her father,

01:41:26.467 --> 01:41:28.628
but I knew that
he would disappoint her,

01:41:28.703 --> 01:41:29.727
and she's better than that.

01:41:29.804 --> 01:41:31.738
So I tried to find her
another father.

01:41:31.806 --> 01:41:33.330
That's completely impossible.

01:41:33.407 --> 01:41:34.840
I'm sure it's very difficult for you.

01:41:34.909 --> 01:41:37.742
Did she tell you any of
the good things that I did?

01:41:37.812 --> 01:41:39.109
'Cause I did a lot of good things.

01:41:39.180 --> 01:41:40.169
I just need the license-

01:41:40.248 --> 01:41:42.910
She's always had
a warm home, food-

01:41:42.984 --> 01:41:45.214
- Lady-
- clothing-

01:41:45.286 --> 01:41:46.480
Lady-

01:41:46.554 --> 01:41:48.715
The best school system.
Did she tell you that?!

01:41:48.789 --> 01:41:51.349
No, ma'am.
Gimme that license, please.

01:41:51.425 --> 01:41:52.357
All right!

01:41:52.426 --> 01:41:54.223
Thank you.

01:41:55.363 --> 01:41:57.797
You know,
she could have been an actress,

01:41:57.865 --> 01:41:59.924
instead she wants
to go away to college.

01:42:00.001 --> 01:42:01.866
She's telling me that
I have to let her go.

01:42:01.936 --> 01:42:03.699
Well, it's always been
just the two of us,

01:42:03.771 --> 01:42:06.137
and that is very hard.

01:42:06.207 --> 01:42:07.572
I don't get it.

01:42:07.642 --> 01:42:12.477
Doesn't she know
I- I would do anything for her?

01:42:12.546 --> 01:42:14.878
I mean, I love her.

01:42:14.949 --> 01:42:17.577
She is the reason I was born.

01:42:17.652 --> 01:42:20.177
Doesn't she understand
that I would do anything for her?

01:42:25.559 --> 01:42:27.083
Then you know what to do.

01:42:35.369 --> 01:42:36.631
Yeah.

01:42:46.280 --> 01:42:48.271
I'll tell you what.

01:42:48.349 --> 01:42:50.112
This is what I'm going to do for you.

01:42:50.184 --> 01:42:51.276
I'm gonna let you go.

01:42:51.352 --> 01:42:52.284
Ok.

